+            <div class="story-text">
+                <p>Some love stories begin with a grand entrance. Ours? Well, let's just say it involved a lot of laughs, a few adventures, and the undeniable realization that we were better together than apart.</p>
+                <p>From our first date to the proposal, every moment has been an adventure. Anna brought her competitive fire (honed on the lacrosse field, naturally), and Will brought... well, Will brought himself, and somehow that was enough.</p>
+                <p>Now we're ready for the biggest adventure of all &mdash; and we want you there to celebrate with us in beautiful Cape May.</p>
