+                <div class="travel-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9992;</div>
+                <h4>By Air</h4>
+                <p><strong>Atlantic City International Airport (ACY)</strong> is the closest airport, about 45 minutes from Cape May. Philadelphia International (PHL) is about 2.5 hours away.</p>
+            </div>
+            <div class="travel-card">
+                <div class="travel-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#128663;</div>
+                <h4>By Car</h4>
+                <p>Cape May is at the very southern tip of the Garden State Parkway. From Philadelphia, take the Atlantic City Expressway to the GSP South. From NYC, take the NJ Turnpike to GSP South.</p>
+            </div>
+            <div class="travel-card">
+                <div class="travel-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#127968;</div>
+                <h4>Accommodations</h4>
+                <p>We have a room block at <strong>Congress Hall</strong>. Use our booking code when making your reservation. Cape May also offers charming B&Bs and vacation rentals &mdash; you can't go wrong!</p>
+            </div>
+            <div class="travel-card">
+                <div class="travel-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#128664;</div>
+                <h4>Getting Around</h4>
+                <p>Cape May is very walkable! Rent bikes from one of several local shops, or use the Cape May trolley. Uber/Lyft are available but limited &mdash; plan ahead for late-night rides.</p>
+            </div>
+        </div>
+    </div>
